{\*\cs13\fs20\b0\i Lavender Hack}{\*\cs11\fs20 , most of the conversion involves converting monster armor class and using abstract values for treasure rather than a gold piece standard. Both of which aren\rquote t too difficult to manage.\par Not sure if }
